exports[`streaming: chat-completions → vertex-anthropic > complexReasoningRequest > streaming 1`] = `
"data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"content":"# Digital Clock Digit Analysis\\n\\nLet me work through this systematically by counting how often each digit (0-9) appears in a 24-hour cycle.\\n\\n## Breaking Down the Clock Format: HH:MM\\n\\n**Hours: 00-23** (24 values)\\n**Minutes: 00-59** (60 values)\\n**Total times in 24 hours: 1,440**\\n\\nEach time displays 4 digits (ignoring the colon).\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Counting Each Digit\\n\\nLet me count occurrences in each position:\\n\\n### **Hours (00-23):**\\n- **0**: 00, 01-09, 10, 20 = 11 times\\n- **1**: 01, 10-19 = 11 times\\n- **2**: 02, 12, 20-23 = 6 times\\n- **3-9**: 03-09, 13-19, 23 = 1 time each (7 digits × 1 = 7)\\n\\n### **Minutes (00-59):**\\n- Each digit appears equally in the **ones place**: 6 times each (0,10,20,30,40,50 for the digit 0, etc.)\\n- **Tens place**: 0 appears 10 times (00-09), 1-5 each appear 10 times (10-19, 20-29, etc.)\\n\\n**Minutes digit totals:**\\n- **0**: 10 + 6 = 16 times\\n- **1-5**: 10 + 6 = 16 times each\\n- **6-9**: 0 + 6 = 6 times each\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Total Counts (per 24-hour period)\\n\\n| Digit | Hours | Minutes | Total |\\n|-------|-------|---------|-------|\\n| **0** | 11 | 16 | **27** |\\n| **1** | 11 | 16 | **27** |\\n| **2** | 6 | 16 | **22** |\\n| **3** | 1 | 16 | **17** |\\n| **4** | 1 | 16 | **17** |\\n| **5** | 1 | 16 | **17** |\\n| **6** | 1 | 6 | **7** |\\n| **7** | 1 | 6 | **7** |\\n| **8** | 1 | 6 | **7** |\\n| **9** | 1 | 6 | **7** |\\n\\n**Total digits displayed: 5,760** (1,440 times × 4 digits)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Results\\n\\n**🏆 MOST COMMON: 0 and 1** (tied)\\n- **27 occurrences each**\\n- **Percentage: 27/5,760 = 0.469% each**\\n\\n**📉 RAREST: 6, 7, 8, and 9** (tied)\\n- **7 occurrences each**\\n- **Percentage: 7/5,760 = 0.122% each**\\n\\nThe most common digits are **2.7x more frequent** than the rarest digits!","role":"assistant"},"finish_reason":"stop","index":0}],"id":"msg_vrtx_01A5DSLSPNjSvHWzeMVs6E23","model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","object":"chat.completion.chunk","usage":{"completion_tokens":765,"prompt_tokens":80,"prompt_tokens_details":{"cached_tokens":0},"total_tokens":845}}

data: [DONE]

"
`;

